videos.description: Monte Morris drives to hoop and flips in shot for 2.
videos.headline: Morris powers in for the layup

videos.description: Nazareth Mitrou-Long drives to the hoop and makes the finger roll.
videos.headline: Mitrou-Long finishes with finger roll

videos.description: Desmond Bane beats his defenders and finishes with finger roll.
videos.headline: TCU's Bane drives the lane for the layup

videos.description: Vladimir Brodziansky sets the pick and then receives pass for dunk.
videos.headline: TCU pick and roll works to perfection

videos.description: Nazareth Mitrou-Long hits the 3 from the wing to give ISU a 32-23 lead.
videos.headline: Mitrou-Long buries the 3-pointer

videos.description: Donovan Jackson drains the 3-pointer from the top of the key to give Iowa State a 35-25 lead.
videos.headline: ISU's Jackson hits from 3

videos.description: Solomon Young takes the behind the back pass from Deonte Burton and finishes with the layup.
videos.headline: Burton to Young a thing of beauty

videos.description: Donovan Jackson takes it all the way for the layup in Iowa State's big win over TCU.
videos.headline: Robinson swoops in for two

videos.description: Deonte Burton scores a game-high 22 points and Monte Morris puts up 15 of his own to lead No. 23 Iowa State to an 84-63 win over TCU in the Big 12 semifinals.
videos.headline: Iowa State makes easy work of TCU
